description:
watch the video for my new song "outside looking in"! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_3_gii4-WMU

at last my diehard childhood love of things like erb and sonic the hedgehog has produced something of value [citation needed]. makes sense that when i finally get to put my announcer impression to good use i'm rusty as hell.

used by siivagunner, cited by knowyourmeme, stolen by tiktok (it's chill, honest. so millions of people saw my shitpost, what, i'm gonna be mad about that?)

hey did you know that the coughing baby image comes from an actual video of the kid coughing? cause i sure didn't before i made this.

- beat: sonic forces ost theme of infinite https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XKjOJuPjiu4
